data.description: Welcome to 1496 West Vernon Ave, a fantastic investment opportunity in the heart of Los Angeles. This well maintained duplex offers two spacious units, each with its own unique charm. Unit 1 features 4 bedroom and 2 bathroom, providing ample space for a growing family. The open floor plan and well design layout make it comfortable and inviting living space. The unit has been meticulously cared. Unit 2 offer 2 bedroom and 1 bathroom, making it an excellent choice and a cozy and manageable living space. The property's location is a standout feature, as it is conveniently situated in a sought-after neighborhood of Los Angeles. Residents enjoy easy access to schools, shopping, dining and public transportation, making it an attractive option. With ample parking space available on the property, you will appreciate the convenience adding to the property's overall appeal, offering an opportunity for an investor looking for a turnkey investment.   Don't miss out on this exceptional investment property in Los Angeles and explore the potential of this duplex as a valuable addition to your real estate portfolio.
